oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Festival of American Fiddle Tunes (1993)

oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red and brown on yellow) announcing the 1993 Festival of American Fiddle Tunes featuring masters of traditional music at the McCurdy Pavilion on July 2 and 3. Poster features a metal photoplate of a violinist (fiddle player).
